data.description: Nestled in the serene neighborhood of Hillbrook, this charming Cape Cod residence boasts a timeless brick exterior and a welcoming ambiance. Featuring 2 bedrooms and 1 bath, this home exudes classic appeal with hardwood floors throughout. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a cozy living area illuminated by large windows that usher in abundant natural light. An arched doorway leads gracefully into the formal dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings. Adjacent to the dining room is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with ample cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops. The entry level hosts a comfortable bedroom and a full bath for added convenience. Ascend to the upper level to discover an expansive bedroom offering ample space and privacy. The lower level presents a versatile family room illuminated by recessed lighting and adorned with resilient vinyl floors, ideal for relaxation or entertainment. Step outside to the stone patio overlooking the standout feature of this property: a flat backyard, providing ample opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. Additional highlights include a shed for extra storage and a paved driveway for convenient parking. This home's prime location offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes, ensuring a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Experience the allure of Hillbrook living in this inviting Cape Cod retreat.
